item.title: The Great British Big Band Tour
item.author: Felix Editor,CATNIP FELIX,Issie Barret,
item.description: O n the 1st of July 2016 in the pouring rain, our two minibuses, ‘Party Bus’ and ‘Stealth Bus’ set off from Imperial College. Windscreen wipers on full pelt, it was a truly British start to the Great British Big Band Tour. Over the next ten days we would travel through rain, shine and everything …
